- I just want to make the read value with milliseconds usable by the algorithm class instead of throwing an exception `could not be parsed`. So in the new commit I removed `private` for `Property` A change to the `private LocalDateTime getDateTime()` function, which is an attempt of mine in the past, and it turns out that this change is not necessary. I changed the description of the documentation synchronously.
